I move to amend HB3056
Of the printed Bill
Page 1 Section 1 Lines 16
Of the Engrossed Bill
By unstriking subsection "A".
Page 2, Section 1, Lines 9.5:
By inserting the following language, "B. Any producer or seller of raw,
unpasteurized milk, sold pursuant to this section, shall not be liable for
any incidental illness due to the consumption of raw, unpasteurized milk
by a consumer."
